content.p: Abi Manohoran, a BSc Nutrition student, talks about the Malaysia Campus, what her course consists of and how an interest in food played a part in choosing her degree. Marissa Aliah Binti Zainal is a second-year student in Plant Biotechnology. Marissa talks about her interest in genetics, her favourite modules and what she loves about campus life. Samson Baranzan is doing an MSc in Crop Biotechnology and Entrepreneurship. He talks about what he hopes to do with his degree why he recommends studying at Nottingham. telephone: +6 (03) 8924 8000 fax: +6 (03) 8924 8018
